page.title: 10My Day
page.content: After dinner we sometimes play rounders. I like being in the batting team because it's more exciting. Then we go back indoors and do science or geography and before you know it,it's time to go home. Once back home again I get ready for recorder lesson at 4.45p.m. When my lesson is over I rollerboot for 10 minutes. Then I have tea. I like egg salad followed by Black Forest Gateau. Then I watch cartoons on the television.I like Mickey Mouse. Soon after that it's time for bed.I get washed, hop into bed and go to sleep.
